    Morse encoder and decoder witten in x86 for the seek
    of learning and having fun.

    $ mrs [mode] "[message]"

    ~ Mode: either m for going from Morse to text, or t to do
    the opposite.

    ~ Notes:
    * About the code: uses tabs of 8 bytes.
    * The output always gives an extra space i.e. "a" -> ".- "

